{"tid":1620743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭去信美國參議員憂人權民主法案　Rick Scott：內容空泛、習近平又一棋子","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:54:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"754c500513f6f51faae5380903a902b081040f60","tid":1620743,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭去信美國參議員憂人權民主法案　斯科特：內容空泛、習近平又一棋子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%86%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E7%89%B9-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E7%A9%BA%E6%B3%9B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%80%E6%A3%8B%E5%AD%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2586%2582%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%2589%25B9-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B3%259B-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A3%258B%25E5%25AD%2590%2F&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=3e53f681\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2586%2582%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%2589%25B9-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B3%259B-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A3%258B%25E5%25AD%2590%2F&h=ef922bd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%86%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E7%89%B9-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E7%A9%BA%E6%B3%9B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%80%E6%A3%8B%E5%AD%90/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前到香港觀察示威情況的美國共和黨參議員斯科特表示，收到行政長官林鄭月娥一封信件，對方重申珍惜自由、民主等價值，又表達對美國《香港人權與民主法案》的擔憂。但斯科特批評信件內容空泛，又指林鄭發信之時，有香港青年被實彈打中，加上政府考慮立《禁蒙面法》，質疑林鄭只是中國國家主席習近平又一棋子(another pawn)。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨參議員斯科特 (Rick Scott)今日在個人網站透露，早前來港時曾經與林鄭月娥、建制派領袖等人士會面，形容林鄭月娥當時「連對於港人基本人權的疑問也無法回答」。斯科特稱，當地星期四他再收到林鄭月娥的跟進信件，信中林鄭月娥稱會珍惜自由、民主等價值及香港與美國的夥伴關係，另外又擔心美國國會推動《香港人權與民主法案》會對香港作為國際商業樞紐不利。<br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>斯科特批評，林鄭的信件內容只是充塞更多的空話，反映對方不重視人權，甚至拒絕市民和平集會的權利。他提到在林鄭發信之時，有香港青年被實彈打中，加上政府考慮立《禁蒙面法》。他形容林鄭月娥只是國家主席習近平在全球稱霸遊戲中又一棋子，又對香港沒有能與民眾站在一起的強大領袖感到失望，但他強調，美國將致力協助港人抗爭，不會退縮。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"faddf37f149b093aaf513523ea3a1c27df0df61e","tid":1620743,"uid":294343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"廢話呃自己就得"},{"pid":"6854a19807c809bfcb62b042887cd7b8d2458c3f","tid":1620743,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca41c9efbf336bf5dd13d38d2172975f44768fe","tid":1620743,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<br />\n讓共產黨親自解決林鄭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}